Question
========

If we take 2 rings at a time from a set of 5 (numbered 1 to 5), how many possible outcomes are there?

Answerlist
----------

* 2
* 5
* 10
* 20

Solution
========

Answerlist
----------

* 2: Incorrect
* 5: Incorrect
* 10: Correct
* 20: Incorrect
